---
const steps = [
  "Connect to your Artifactory instance",
  "Select what to migrate",
  "Click startâ€”we handle the rest",
  "Verify with built-in integrity checks",
];
---

<section id="migration" class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
      Migrate from Artifactory in an afternoon
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      Our built-in migration tool handles everything&mdash;repositories, artifacts, metadata, users, and permissions.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Left: Steps -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        {steps.map((step, i) => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">
              {i + 1}
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 pt-1">{step}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Placeholder screenshot -->
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[280px]">
        <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Migration tool screenshot</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Proof point -->
    <blockquote class="mt-12 border-l-4 border-brand pl-6 text-gray-600 italic max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Migrate 50,000+ artifacts with full metadata preservation. Resume interrupted migrations automatically. Zero data loss guaranteed.
    </blockquote>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-10">
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-md border-2 border-brand text-brand font-semibold hover:bg-brand hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        See Migration Docs
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@artifactkeeper.com"
        class="text-brand font-semibold hover:underline"
      >
        Book a Migration Consultation &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
